OL,3,CChief constable backs calls for
OL,4,CChinook crash public inquiry
OL,6,FUTV can reveal that the Chief
OL,7,FConstable of the PSNI has given his
OL,8,Fbacking to families campaigning for a
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry into the Chinook
OL,10,FHelicopter crash in 1994.
OL,12,FTen high ranking RUC officers from
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland were among 29 people
OL,14,Fkilled when the helicopter carrying
OL,15,Fsecurity personnel to a conference in
OL,16,FScotland came down on the Mull of
OL,17,FKintyre.
OL,19,FFiles on relating to the tragedy have
OL,20,Fbeen locked away for 100 years.
