OL,3,CChief constable backs calls for
OL,4,CChinook crash public inquiry
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Secretary of State
OL,7,Ffor Northern Ireland, PSNI Chief
OL,8,FConstable Jon Boutcher says, "A lack
OL,9,Fof official transparency is adding to
OL,10,Fthe suffering of these families."
OL,12,FHe asks Hilary Benn to use ".... any
OL,13,Finfluence you are able upon cabinet
OL,14,Fcolleagues and government officials,
OL,15,Fto enable the families to get answers
OL,16,Fto the many questions they have."
OL,18,FDes Conroy lost his father, RUC Chief
OL,19,FSuperintendent Desmond Conroy in the
OL,20,Ftragedy.
