OL,6,FHe says the support of Jon Boutcher
OL,7,Fand the PSNI has given the bereaved a
OL,8,Fsense of hope.
OL,10,F"It's massive to my family and all the
OL,11,Ffamilies, hopefully it is the turning
OL,12,Fof the corner. We need to know why
OL,13,Fthese 29 dedicated individuals who
OL,14,Fserved their country were put on this
OL,15,Faircraft."
OL,17,FThe helicopter's two pilots had been
OL,18,Fblamed for the crash but 17 years
OL,19,Flater they were exonerated.
