OL,6,FIn a statement the MOD said: "The Mull
OL,7,Fof Kintyre crash was a tragic
OL,8,Faccident, and our thoughts and
OL,9,Fsympathies remain with the families,
OL,10,Ffriends and colleagues of all those
OL,11,Fwho died.
OL,13,F"We understand that the lack of
OL,14,Fcertainty about the cause of the crash
OL,15,Fhas added to the distress of the
OL,16,Ffamilies.
