OL,3,CChief constable backs calls for
OL,4,CChinook crash public inquiry
OL,6,F"We provided a detailed and considered
OL,7,Fresponse to the pre-action protocol
OL,8,Fletter stating the reasons why we
OL,9,Fcannot accept the demand for
OL,10,Festablishing a new Public Inquiry.
OL,11,FIt's unlikely that a Public Inquiry
OL,12,Fwould identify any new evidence or
OL,13,Freach new conclusions on the basis of
OL,14,Fexisting evidence.
OL,16,F"The accident has already been the
OL,17,Fsubject of six inquiries and
OL,18,Finvestigations, including an
OL,19,Findependent Judge-led review."
